LEATHER GODESSES OF PHOBOS:

                          SOLUTION


(c) 1992 Erik Futtrup, Denmark and Twan Lintermans, Holland


The commands are separated by a '-' sign and [] include comment
and tips to understand the solution better! Let's start:

[male version]-nw-take stool-urinate-smell [spot no
1]-se-inventory-wait-smell food [spot no 2]-take all-open
door-s-read sign-open south door-s-take paper-read paper [without
the machine parts it reads: hissing frightens flytraps]-ask trent
about goddesses-n-u-look through window-light flashlight-n-smell
[spot no 3]-drop stool-stand on stool-take basket-get off
stool-take stool-put all in basket-stand on circle-hiss [remember
the paper?]-w-[when trent gives you the matchbook use this
command: read matchbook]-take jar-stand on circle-take sword-look
through viewport-s-mount horse-w-dismount horse-take suit-wear
suit-open hatch-n-smell [spot no 5]-hit thorbast with sword-again
[until it reads: '..., knocking the sword out of Thorbast's
hands! It drifts toward you, spinning slowly.']-take his
sword-throw his sword to thorbast-hit monster with sword-untie
woman-follow woman-open door-e-s-s-mount horse-e-dismount
horse-w-w-w-stand on circle-[teleported to 'ruin', where you meet
a frog]-examine frog-w-w-nw-examine painting-show painting to
mouse-take mouse-give mouse to trent-s-stand on
circle-u-u-n-stand on circle-e-e-take can-nw-offer flashlight to
salesman-take odd machine-knock on door-d-put all in cage-wait
[...straps you down]-wait [...flips the huge red power
switch]-examine trent-examine female gorilla-kiss female
gorilla-take all-take food-eat food [remember smell no 2!]-bend
bars-exit cage-untie me-untie trent-drop all-turn switch-get off
slab-take all-stand on circle-push knob-open box-take
coin-examine coin-se-stand on circle-s-open machine [this is the
tee-remover!]-examine jar-read jar-put jar in machine-close
machine-turn machine on-open machine-take jar-put unangling cream
on angle-put all in basket-take angle-n-enter barge-press
purple-press orange [reading the text on the buttons helps to
understand their use]-wait-wait-wait-wait-press orange-exit
barge-n-take all-read message [it can be decoded by going four
letters back in the alphabet (e.g. d becomes a) and reading the
message from right to left; it says: 'your mission is to contact
wife number 3137 of the sultan and get the secret map -- identify
yourself to her by asking her to kiss your kneecaps'; the number
is random and must be read from right to left (without decoding,
here: 7313)]-s-enter barge-push orange-again-exit
barge-s-e-e-w-s-n-w-n-enter barge-push orange-wait-wait-push
orange-exit barge-e-s-take clothes pin-n-e-look into
well-se-u-stand on circle-wait-s-u-u-stand on circle-e-put pin on
nose-put lip balm on lips-drop all-close eyes-put hands on
ears-kiss frog-take all-w-w-stand on circle-u-n-stand on
circle-drop
message,sword,matchbook,stool,blender,photo,hose,machine,jar,tray-drop painting,paper-w-enter barge-push
orange-wait-wait-wait-wait-press orange-exit barge-press orange
[you should be outside the barge!!]-w-take rabbit-put black stain
on circle-stand on circle-s-take all-n-ne-u-take sheet-tear
sheet-tie strips together-tie rope to bed-throw rope out of
window-wait-wait [honour your brave friend!]-take headlight-go
down the stairs-e-take trellis-move sod-stand on circle-n-stand
on circle-drop sack,rake,trellis-e-enter well-exit
barge-s-se-read sign-give coin to penguin-se-n-wrap baby in
blanket-take baby-put baby in basket-s-s-read sign-look through
window-put baby on stoop-wait-wait-open door-enter igloo-take
cotton balls-ne-n-nw-w-stand on circle-w-stand on
circle-ne-e-stand on circle-n-stand on circle-give cotton balls
to trent-give headlight to trent-give angle to trent-remove
pin-take hose-give hose to trent-take blender-give blender to
trent-take photo-read photo-give photo to trent-drop all-take
coin-ne-yes-say "riddle"-w-7313 [use your decoded number from the
coded message!]-w-smell [spot no 4]-wait-wife,kiss my
kneecaps-take all-d [here we start our voyage through the
catacombs]-nw-se-ne-clap-e-ne-ne-hop-clap-kweepa-se-d-nw-
clap-ne-n-hop-s-clap-ne-kweepa-u-nw-clap-take phone
book-hop-nw-s-clap-se-kweepa-se-d-clap-hop-e-n-w-clap-e-w-
kweepa-hop-clap-sw-sw-take raft-clap-n-ne-hop-kweepa-clap-e-
nw-n-u [finally, we made it out of this mess!]-n-e-se-u-stand 
on circle-d-s-u-u-stand on circle-n-n-n-put raft in canal-enter
raft-wait-wait-wait-wait-wait-wait-grab dock-s-e-s-buy exit-give
coin to proprietor-search dust-n-open tube-take circle-drop
circle-stand on circle-smell [spot no 6]-wait-wait-give blender
to trent [he'll ask you for it]-give hose to trent-give cotton
balls to trent-give angle to trent-give headlight to trent-give
mouse to trent-give photo to trent-give phone book to trent [spot
no 7]-[this concludes the game and gives you the rank of
Interplanetary Emperor].
